{
  "stem": "4662.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was only about 13 at that time, so I didn't take any notice of him, of course.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's, that's the first time I saw him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how old were you then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about 18.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you didn't get married then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I got-- I saw him once before when a few years younger, when he was 13 and I was 15.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't-- it wasn't anything special.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just didn't take any notice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was so young, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this time, when you went to, to see your, your--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandparents?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That time?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This time, I got engaged to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he took me out at evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, he had a girlfriend, so we went both together to say to her he couldn't go, because he had friends from England.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he took-- we went out dancing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was-- I didn't understand him, he didn't understand me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we danced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, I don't know how it happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in two days time, he asked me to marry him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was sleeping with an aunt at my grandparents' place, and they brought me a bowl of flowers up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were old flowers that they had downstairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, what's this in honor of?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, well, you got engaged to Louis De Groot last night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I did not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, oh yes, you did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the-- I was so shy, I didn't even dare to say that's not true.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said, oh, that's possible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's the way it remained.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] It's silly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I won a-- I won a prize on television with this story once too, when we first came to Canada thirty years ago.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
